title: MisterMusic Show 358 - indie, alternative, rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 358 [2 hours] 192kbps MP3-



New music this week from Trails and Ways, The Jungle Giants, and Matt Nathanson.
Plus a big hit from June 1974 is the "Oldie of the Week".
It's a blend of indie, alternative and classic hits from over 5 decades.

Broadcasting weekly and heard globally on the web on Rock XS Radio.
